{"tid":2211785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱利安尼：沒有比中共更適合RICO法案的了，因為中共是黑幫！","createTime":"2020-09-21T10:36:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T11:26:13.000Z","uid":294518,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8f7b2bc11f14efa1a3619a788e0b0fce5f4a034","tid":2211785,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:36:41.000Z","msg":"朱利安尼：沒有比中共更適合RICO法案的了，因為中共是黑幫中的黑幫！<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AD%AF%E8%BF%AA%C2%B7%E6%9C%B1%E5%88%A9%E5%AE%89%E5%B0%BC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E9%25AD%25AF%25E8%25BF%25AA%25C2%25B7%25E6%259C%25B1%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%25AE%2589%25E5%25B0%25BC&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=bf9e432f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%AD%AF%E8%BF%AA%C2%B7%E6%9C%B1%E5%88%A9%E5%AE%89%E5%B0%BC</a><br />\n<br />\n朱利亞尼最初擔任聯邦檢察官，用RICO 法案起訴了許多高知名度的黑社會犯罪集團首腦。<br />\n<br />\n他接著在1994年至2001年間擔任8年紐約市市長，於市長任內致力於降低犯罪率並改善城市生活的品質。在世界貿易中心遭受恐怖攻擊的九一一事件期間，擔任市長的朱利安尼以他突出的坐鎮領導能力而聞名全球。<br />\n<br />\n訪問中，他舉了他職業生涯中利用RICO法案打擊外籍有組織犯罪和紐約黑幫滲透工會的的例子，如Teamster工會和紐約服裝行業工會。然後他就説了這番話。後面還説了他已經掌握<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">中共賄賂拜登的證據</span></span>，下次會帶著文件來。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BoDiplo/status/1307485651256979458?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBoDiplo%2Fstatus%2F1307485651256979458%3Fs%3D20&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=e2fc70ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBoDiplo%2Fstatus%2F1307485651256979458%3Fs%3D20&h=8d107d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BoDiplo/status/1307485651256979458?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"24de08aba7c3b8d9f7df94ebea54ac21d2748526","tid":2211785,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34827b5e5a3d5345c469dee53390682a893ca0b1","tid":2211785,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:39:22.000Z","msg":"朱利安尼先生说，没有比中共更合适RICO法案的了。<br />\n因为中共在美国犯罪，巨额的洗钱以及偷盗。<br />\n一旦RICO法案执行，中共所有的财产将被没收。<br />\n最关键是的，朱利安尼先生说他自己当年就是用过这个法案的，消滅紐約5大黑幫。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/WlKD6iuxiZqBvm7/status/1307416536349638659?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWlKD6iuxiZqBvm7%2Fstatus%2F1307416536349638659%3Fs%3D20&d=nIll2RoSQXmni3IMQi%2BZogx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=05a8c637\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FWlKD6iuxiZqBvm7%2Fstatus%2F1307416536349638659%3Fs%3D20&h=3510d792\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/WlKD6iuxiZqBvm7/status/1307416536349638659?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"5b31e6f6073f9900a80947a531d4020a66391d71","tid":2211785,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}